  {
    stat: 'Bayonne HVAC Team',
    description: '3-truck operation losing emergency calls to bigger companies with 24/7 answering services. Missed 40% of after-hours inquiries. After foundation rebuild + AI dispatcher: 0 missed calls, 15-second average text-back time, 3.4x job volume growth. Owner said: "We wake up to booked schedules now."',
