    description: 'Family-owned shop with stellar work but 9 Google reviews total. Customers loved them but never remembered to post feedback. After review engine with QR cards + text automation: 118 new 5-star reviews in 90 days, #2 in Map Pack for "auto repair Jersey City," 67% increase in first-time customers.',
  },
  {
    stat: 'Union City Plumbing',
    description: 'Emergency calls flooded the owner\'s personal cell, including spam and price shoppers. Dispatch team overwhelmed screening inquiries. After CRM routing + AI triage: 22% decrease in dispatch labor hours, qualified leads routed instantly, spam filtered automatically. "I got my nights back," owner said.',
  },
  {
    stat: 'Hoboken Electrical Contractors',
    description: 'One-time service calls, no follow-up, no recurring revenue. After maintenance membership automation + nurture flows: $240K additional revenue in 6 months from HVAC tune-up memberships, seasonal reminders, and referral incentives. Recurring revenue now 31% of total business.',
